      "text": "- The `security-expert` agent's system prompt or execution logic might heavily prioritize the \"no changes\" instruction, treating file creation (even for the audit doc) as a \"change\" to be avoided.\n\n## Investigation Results\n\n**Status**: Verified / Root Cause Identified\n\nThe issue is caused by the interaction between the Planner's interpretation of \"no changes\" and the `ExecutionLoop`'s fallback behavior.",
